            <description><![CDATA[【半天憋不出一句祝福语，请全国护士来当我的嘴替<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[酷]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_ku-774d16f5ce.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[求饶]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a2qiurao-7ad34b9c84.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】护士节到了，怎么夸？护士不过也是一群医院里的打工人，打针发药，倒屎倒尿，日常三班倒，经常熬通宵。今天不整花里胡哨的，就祝你节日不表演，夜班准时下，备办不被叫，搭班特靠谱，打针不被骂，灌肠不被喷，考试都通过，帅哥靓女争着要！祝你自由，祝你健康，祝你快乐。护士节快乐！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抱一抱]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/co_a1hug-f3910d0e88.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8A%A4%E5%A3%AB%E8%8A%82%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E5%A4%B8%E8%B5%9E%E7%A5%9D%E7%A6%8F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8A%A4%E5%A3%AB%E8%8A%82%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E5%A4%B8%E8%B5%9E%E7%A5%9D%E7%A6%8F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#护士节有效夸赞祝福#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4900502358654999" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hdvc5t6oksj21hc0u0jvq.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/HlMc5w8Ggx085nfwmWaA01041200Hgyc0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1683944074&amp;ssig=TZC%2Fj3B1bD&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/QPKG4gGugx085nfvQgMg01041200lDhW0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1683944074&amp;ssig=HLPaM%2FoEXr&amp;KID=unistore,video"><s